snippet.title: Backrooms Society - Free Demo now live on steam!
snippet.description:
Wishlist and download demo on steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2304620/Backrooms_Society/
Join our Discord for updates: https://discord.gg/vpXzH32JTK

Backrooms Society is a 1-8 player co-op horror game, it shows the backrooms game genre in a different light. Once you find yourself in the backrooms there is no way out; so instead of searching for an escape: make use of your new surroundings, gather resources, survive and build a new society with the countless others who has suffered the same fate as you.


subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/imepsinnn

thank you!
